                      <p>Foll. <locus from="1" to="9">1-9</locus> and <locus from="40" to="49">40-49</locus> have been written by a different hand, and may be of the <date notBefore="0800" notAfter="0900" calendar="Gregorian">ixth cent.</date> Fol. <locus from="10a">10a</locus> has been retouched by the same hand.</p>
                    </item>
                  <item n="2" xml:id="addition2">
                    <locus from="88b" to="88b"/>
                    <p>On <locus from="88b" to="88b">fol. 88b</locus> a reader called <persName ref="">Bar-saumā</persName> has written his name,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܒܪܨܘܡܐ</foreign>.</p>
